title: [Switch Hits, Showroom]
description: Threads of ragged silk dangle from above like drifting spiderwebs.  Their slow unraveling has made a mockery of the tent's ceiling, which allows in ragged threads of sunlight to spill onto the hard-packed dirt floor below.  The fabric walls are lined with decaying shelves of burled wood, which boast a collection of incongruously well-tended wares.
